task.summary: Finished Deck, DiscardPile, FoundationPile, and WastePile.
Changed FoundationPile, WastePile, and Deck implementations

Added "dragging". It just changes the cursor to a small version of the card. All I have right now for that. Added a win menu item to show we can win the game. When a King is placed inside of a foundation pile, the back now shows to symbolize locking (which has also been implemented).
Added the win condition. If you "win" then you get a popup dialog that says you won.
